author: ehu
msg: Prefer stringbufs over Neon buffers because they are pool bound.
(svn_ra_dav__get_props): Build the request body in a stringbuf instead
of a Neon buffer; both can realloc, but stringbufs are pool bound.
Also use SVN_ERR now that don't have manually tracked resources anymore.
(append_setprop): Renamed from do_setprop() to get closer to the actual
functionality. Changed from Neon buffer to stringbuf useage.
(svn_ra_dav__do_proppatch): Build the request body in a stringbuf instead
